list.abstract: 在ASP.NET应用程序中，Membership 类用于验证用户凭据并管理用户设置（如密码和电子邮件地址）。Membership 类可以独自使用，或者与 FormsAuthentication 一起使用以创建一个完整的 Web 应用程序或网站的用户身份验证系统。Login 控件封装了 Membership 类，从而提供一种便捷的用户验证机制。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, Dave in the membership office, handles quitters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，请找会员服务部的戴维。

yingyinNormal.en: And here is my Justice League membership card. But that doesn't prove I know Batman.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我正义联盟的会员卡，但是这不能证明我认识蝙蝠侠。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, now, do you really need the honorary justice league of America membership card?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你真的需要那张美国荣誉审判联盟的会员卡吗？

yingyinNormal.en: But he told me he checked on our membership just last week, and we were still 400th in line.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但他上周跟我说他看了我们的会员申请，我们还在顺位400多名呢。

yingyinNormal.en: It's all yours. And don't forget your membership proposal. Try picking a more suitable candidate this time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这交给你了，还有不要忘了上交候选人提名。这次尽量挑个更合适的人选。

yingyinNormal.en: The Cult of Tusk. Membership one. But that one disciple just so happens to be the most powerful man in the free world. For now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 塔斯克党，成员，一人。不过那个信徒恰好是自由世界最有权力的人，至少目前还是。

direction_info.description:

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
